16:37:04 INFO gaia_agent.nodes.executor: [executor] calling tool=run_python args={'code': 'import requests\nfrom bs4 import BeautifulSoup\n\ndef get_wikipedia_discography(artist_name):\n    search_url = f"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/{artist_name.replace(\' \', \'_\')}"\n    response = requests.get(search_url, headers={\'User-Agent\': \'Mozilla/5.0\'})\n    if response.status_code != 200:\n        return f"Error: Could not find page for {artist_name}"\n    \n    soup = BeautifulSoup(response.text, \'html.parser\')\n    \n    # Check if there\'s a separate discography page\n    discography_link = soup.find(\'a\', title=lambda x: x and \'discography\' in x.lower())\n    if discography_link and \'discography\' in discography_link.get(\'title\', \'\').lower():\n         disc_url = "https://en.wikipedia.org" + discography_link[\'href\']\n         response = requests.get(disc_url, headers={\'User-Agent\': \'Mozilla/5.0\'})\n         soup = BeautifulSoup(response.text, \'html.parser\')\n\n    return soup.prettify()[:10000] # Return first 10000 chars to identify structure\n\nprint(get_wikipedia_discography("Mercedes Sosa"))\n'}
